I see four questionable assumptions here:

1. The meaning of the Newsgroups: header according to RFC 1036 applies
   to email.
2. News and email are fundamentally the same thing.
3. It is reasonable that software should discard useful
   out-of-band information.
4. Established practice means nothing.
