news for the same thing, and write the tools to allow the distinction to
be made. That is, simply, accept that "same thing" is not the only
viewpoint. Nobody is saying that you must accept "different" as the only
way, just accept it as A way. A tool that allows users to differentiate
can be used in non-differentiating mode, but the obverse is not true.

