in the reader's mind that it might be a Usenet posting.

It absolutely does not matter if the same email message might also have
been posted to Usenet by its author.  If what one has in one's mailbox
is what arrived by email, treat it as email.  If one wishes to post a
follow-up, one posts a follow-up to the specific copy that's in the
News spool area.  Please see more about this in the aforementioned
separate posting.
