In <Pine.SGI.3.91.950328184420.16934A-100000@wong> Ian Russell Ollmann <iano@scripps.edu> writes:



>On Mon, 27 Mar 1995, Myles Kagan wrote:

>> Is PINE or a program like PINE available for the MAC.  I am looking for a
